          <p class="muted">
            No trading system can guarantee outcomes. The goal is to create a
            statistically positive, risk-controlled framework, not certainty.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Which markets does the system trade?</div>
          <p class="muted">
            The focus is primarily on FX pairs and XAU/USD, with specific
            attention to liquidity windows and session overlaps. Additional
            assets may be added depending on demand and research.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Is the system fully automated?</div>
          <p class="muted">
            Yes. Signals are generated by a rules-driven pipeline without
            discretionary overrides. Human input is limited to research,
            configuration, and monitoring.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q">Will there be premium tiers?</div>
          <p class="muted">
            Potentially in the future — for example, deeper analytics,
            regime dashboards, API access to model outputs, or custom
            symbol/risk configurations. For now, the Telegram signal
            channel is free.
